 i support the proposals with regard to the ministry of agriculture and farmers welfare for the year 201718  in my lok sabha constituency  of  lakhimpur  khiriuttar  pradesh  there  is  much  forest  area bordering  which  there  are  a  number  of  villages  where  villagers  carry  out cultivation on their agricultural land  a provision should be made to compensate the loss of crops by wild animals in the present crop insurance scheme    